Frequently Asked Questions

Quick answers to common questions about our platform and services

How do I book a homestay?

Browse our marketplace, select a homestay, and book directly through our secure platform. All bookings are verified and protected.

Can I become a local guide?

Yes! Apply through our community section. We provide training and certification for local guides interested in sharing their knowledge.

Is the platform available in local languages?

Currently available in English and Hindi. We're working on adding more local languages including Santhali and Mundari.

How do you ensure authentic experiences?

All our partners are verified local community members. We use blockchain technology to ensure authenticity and transparency.
